			  	Make the Empire harder and better defended each time the server is reset. Every defeat it suffers, any surviving fleets from the battle (Empire ships) should be respaced to other planets as the Empire strives to defend its holdings. If the Empire loses all its planets and is left with the Fortress and Capital, then any surviving fleets from the planets should be pulled to the next target. By the Capital, the Empire should be exceptionally hard to fight anyway, surviving fleets from the other battles will make it harder.<br />
<br />
Just a thought.			   <P align=right></P>
