			  	heres a meld of two ideas ive seen here.  the AI council and harder empire.<br />
<br />
i say this about AI councils.  have them spontaneously form during the game, and allow them a lot of AI players per coucil to keep a lot of players busy.  aside from having to defeat the empire, all AI councils have to be gone to beat the game.  this will add some entertainment at least.<br />
<br />
for the harder empire, i dont know a lot about how it defends or attacks, so i may mention something that already exists.  i think there should be a bunch of tactics that can be randomly drawn upon for the empire's defense and attack formations.  depending on what is/has been attacked, the formations and tactics get harder.  i also say that the empire should be able to do spy attacks, or attempt to do so, on anyone that is attacking.  also, if no one is attacking the empire at a given time, the empir eitself should be able to attack at will, using similar ships and numbers to that of the person being attacked.<br />
<br />
i got a lot more ideas to make this whole thing better, but those are just the best of them.			   <P align=right></P>
